title: Gritty Fever top Lynx 75-69 in Game 1 of WNBA Finals
text:
> Sports Gritty Fever top Lynx 75-69 in Game 1 of WNBA Finals Minnesota Lynx’s Lindsay Whalen, left, tries to get around Indiana Fever’s Shenise Johnson in the first half of Game 1 of the WNBA basketball finals Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, in Minneapolis. (AP Photo/Jim Mone)
